                </listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#GC">
                <p>When he was hieromnamon, Tittelos son of Artemidoros took care of the works for the andreon and the proedra, together with the hierophylakes.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it" source="http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR">
                <p>Mentre era hieromnamon, Tittelos figlio di Artemidoros ha completato la cura dei lavori dell'andreon e della proedra insieme con gli hierophylakes.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p><!--commented out pending revision-->
                    <!--lists Hieromnamon under whom work undertaken; building work is of Andreon and proedra, perhaps related to gymnasion? cf. Nenci 1991 for context / discussion, offering it as the most recent (p.925) of a series of such inscr., all poss. of a single family - although if so, then C2 seems more likely!; cf. SEG 41.825.--></p>
            </div>
